    "### 1.7 Prediction Horizon and Feature Timing\n",
    "\n",
    "**Prediction Time:** At the point of campaign interaction (when demographic, campaign, and engagement data has been recorded).  \n",
    "**Prediction Horizon:** Whether the customer converts during or immediately after the current campaign.  \n",
    "**Feature Window:** All input features are recorded at or before the prediction moment.  \n",
    "**Leakage Risk:** `ConversionRate` is suspected to be derived from the target variable itself. If it represents the outcome rather than a pre-campaign metric, it must be dropped to prevent data leakage. This will be investigated in Section 4."
   ]
